opped.jpeg|thumb|right|Sotnikova with President [[Vladimir Putin]] after Olympics, 24 February 2014]]\n\n* GP: [[ISU Grand Prix of Figure Skating|Grand Prix]]; CS: [[ISU Challenger Series|Challenger Series]]; JGP: [[ISU Junior Grand Prix|Junior Grand Prix]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! style=\"background-color: #ffdead;\" colspan=10 | International<ref name=isucr/>\n|-\n! Event\n! 07\u201308\n! [[2008\u201309 figure skating season|08\u201309]]\n! [[2009\u201310 figure skating season|09\u201310]]\n! [[2010\u201311 figure skating season|10\u201311]]\n! [[2011\u201312 figure skating season|11\u201312]]\n! [[2012\u201313 figure skating season|12\u201313]]\n! [[2013\u201314 figure skating season|13\u201314]]\n! [[2014\u201315 figure skating season|14\u201315]]\n! [[2015\u201316 figure skating season|15\u201316]]\n|-\n| align=left | [[Figure skating at the Olympic Games|Olympics]] || || || || || || || bgcolor=gold | 1st || ||\n|-\n| align=left | [[World Figure Skating Championships|Worlds]] || || || || || || 9th || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | [[European Figure Skating Championships|Europeans]] || || || || || || bgcolor=silver | 2nd || bgcolor=silver | 2nd || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Grand Prix of Figure Skating Final|Final]] || || || || || || || 5th || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Internationaux de France|Bompard]] || || || || || || || bgcolor=silver | 2nd || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Cup of China]] || || || || || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd || || bgcolor=silver | 2nd || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[NHK Trophy]] || || || || || || || || WD ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Cup of Russia|Rostelecom]] || || || || || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd || 5th || || WD || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|GP}} [[Skate America]] || || || || || || bgcolor=cc9966 | 3rd || || ||\n|-\n| align=left | {{small|CS}} [[Golden Spin of Zagreb|Golden Spin]] || || || || || bgcolor=gold | 1st || || || || 6th\n|-\n| align=l